"User quiet-bold posted:

@sienna-weapon, you're just trying to stir up trouble here. Can't we all just agree that slavery was a terrible thing and that it's great it's been abolished? Why do we have to argue about who did it first or who gets the credit? Let's just move on and focus on making the world a better place.

@moderator, I think @sienna-weapon and @forward-archer are both making valid points. Let's not get too caught up in the details and remember that we're all on the same side here. #peaceandlove"
